 Tanker Explosion in Oshodi-Apapa Exp way. Source: Twitter (@caxtonJP) A Tanker loaded with PMS has been involved in an accident resulting to a Fire Outbreak in Lagos state. The tanker exploded at Toyota Bus Stop along Oshodi-Apapa expressway on Thursday, January 7, 2021. It’s unknown yet if there were casualties as emergency responders battle to contain the fire. [10:19AM] @Abu_Muminah: Fire incident on both sides of Toyota busstop along Oshodi/ Apapa express way..   @TrafficChiefNG pic.twitter.com/MVUxhGFl37 #TrafficChief — #LagosTrafficReports (@TrafficChiefNG) January 7, 2021